structure.unit: COUNTY AND CITY BRIDGES, TUNNELS, AND FERRIES

law.history: Repealed 2009 (1st Extra. Sess.) Ky. Acts ch. 1, sec. 114, effective June 26, 2009. -- Created 1952 Ky. Acts ch. 189, sec. 12, effective June 19, 1952.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Authority of counties, cities and other political subdivisions to lease, lend or sell property to commission.
